Break The Sigma. 
Its time to normalize the silent majority & Mental Health! You're never alone just ask for help 🙏🏼
1-800-273-8255

Please like comment and share someone you know may need to hear this 🙏🏼

🎥 Videographer : @zacharychristopherr 

#help #mentalhealth #postivevibes #makeadifference #selflove #awareness #mentalhealthawareness

node.text: Hope this New’s Story can help motivate someone as we’re all going through this tough time together. Tough times don’t last tough people do! Keep your head up and stay focused there’s a light at the end of every tunnel and the only way you don’t get there is by quitting to early! I’ve done the impossible and I hope my story inspires to keep moving forward! 🇺🇸

node.text:
Left or Right!? 
Here’s my one year transformation 2020 on the left and 2019 on the right! 
2021 my biggest goal is not just to change my physical appearance, but to become the best version of myself. I wanna wake up every day with a purpose and confidence that my actions are only having a positive impact on those around me. For the past 5 years the only happiness I could find was in drugs, girls, and chasing likes/ popularity on social media. You can numb depression and put on a fake smile but we all have flaws and struggles. It’s not a sympathy story, it’s a statement that it’s okay not to be perfect 🙌🏼
2021 I challenge you to accept your flaws, ask for help when you need it, and wake up everyday telling yourself how great you are! Wish you all an amazing year and thank you so much for the love you’ve put into my life. 🤘🏽
